"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64692","Department for Education","false","2014-07-03","<p>The average age at which teachers in publicly-funded schools in England drew their retirement benefits in every year between 2008-09 and 2012-13 was 59.</p>","Yeovil","Mr David Laws",,"2014-07-03T16:47:11.8426798Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64692/answer","Biography information for Mr David Laws","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64692/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64692/answer",,,,,,,,"60","Education","Education","2014-06-30","Teachers: Retirement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, what the average retirement age was for teachers in each of the last five years for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Debbie Abrahams","Oldham East and Saddleworth","Debbie Abrahams","202996"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64693","Department for Education","false","2014-07-08","<p>Registered independent schools must meet the independent school standards. These state that the curriculum must give pupils experience in ‘linguistic, mathematical, scientific, technological, human and social, physical, and aesthetic and creative education.' Science must therefore be included in the curriculum. Ofsted and the independent school inspectorates inspect independent schools against these standards.</p>","Yeovil","Mr David Laws",,"2014-07-08T16:49:46.57712Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64693/answer","Biography information for Mr David Laws","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64693/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64693/answer",,,,,,,,"60","Education","Education","2014-06-30","Creationism and Evolution: Education","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, whether an independent school (a) teaching creationism and (b) failing to teach evolution as an established scientific theory would lead to it receiving a lower rating under the independent schools inspection framework; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Caroline Lucas","Brighton, Pavilion","Caroline Lucas","202970"
